# Issue Management Rules

## Core Principles

- Unresolved problems belong in `docs/issues/`, not only in chat or memory.
- Retired documents belong in `docs/archive/`, not silent deletion.

## Recording Rules

- blockers, technical debt, and known risks go into `docs/issues/`
- replaced or retired documents go into `docs/archive/`
- every archived document should explain its replacement and retirement reason

## Review Questions

- Did this work create unresolved issues that were never recorded?
- Did this work replace old docs without adding an archive note?
